<paragraph id="531C8FCBAA42FF432E293797CAFF5392" pageId="73" pageNumber="74">
(Fig. 
<figureCitation id="6BC7368173253DECC230FAC40DB2DC0C" captionStart="Figure 85" captionStartId="F85" captionText="Figure 85. Distribution of Conostegia lindenii." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.67.6703.figure85" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/96443" pageId="73" pageNumber="74">85</figureCitation>
